https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/105958/', '', 'Carisoprodol, Chlorzoxazone, Tizanidine, Baclofen, Methocarbamol, Chlormezanone', 'Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Flunisolide, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
