of whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/105961/', '', 'Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 'Carisoprodol, Chlorzoxazone, Baclofen, Methocarbamol, Chlormezanone', 1767369485);
